easant sunset color palette;<br></li><li>And not less important, a cute cat!</li></ul><br><i><strong>It's a Cat in Mars, do I need to say anything else?</strong></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655700/extras/8d3043a5d7b7516d3afde609a05d1a1b.poster.avif?t=1686680433\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655700/extras/8d3043a5d7b7516d3afde609a05d1a1b.webm?t=1686680433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655700/extras/8d3043a5d7b7516d3afde609a05d1a1b.mp4?t=1686680433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
